===Proper noun===
'''Krishna'''
#the divine speaker of ''Bhagavad-gita.'' In [[Hindu]] theology, he is sometimes regarded as the eighth [[avatar]] of [[Vishnu]] and sometimes as the very origin of Vishnu. He is usually depicted playing the flute and his skin complexion is depicted as blue.
#a river in southern [[India]]

